@Fayed_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5194

### List published listings (paged)
GET {{Fayed_API_HostAddress}}/api/listings?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get the category tree
GET {{Fayed_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories/tree
Accept: application/json

### Create a category
POST {{Fayed_API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rubber",
  "parentId": null
}

###
